{"tid":897765,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【好有畫面】台中屋苑取名「三上悠雅」 與日本 AV 女優撞名","createTime":"2018-11-11T07:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T08:54:41.000Z","uid":29625,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d2c8d69fbb729d8c5be8a3e55207c8fd3ec39e","tid":897765,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"香港的地產發展商一向充滿充作力量同幻想，總為屋苑想出會嚇人一跳的名字，當大家都以為本港近年來新落成的私人住宅名稱已經夠創意時，原來與台灣發展商相比，只是「小巫見大巫」，最近台中就有一個新屋苑取名為「三上悠雅」，與著名日本 AV 天后「三上悠亞」撞名！<br />\n<br />\n由台灣「三上建設」於大雅區新建的屋苑位於農業區，生活氣氛平靜樸實，給人一種悠閒的感覺，取名為「三上悠雅」本來十分貼切，奈何這個名字卻與日本 AV 天后「三上悠亞」碰巧撞名。有台灣傳媒報道，公司當初提供了數個名稱供老闆選擇，對方千挑萬選終選擇了「三上悠雅」這個名字，老闆原本並不知道這個名稱的「隱藏含義」，後來了解真相後也沒有介意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/5/5fcd5db52ddfea2b9267ed2d5fb00a31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F5%2F5fcd5db52ddfea2b9267ed2d5fb00a31.jpg&h=7809cda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/8/8614ae1baa69934ae70080408029164e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F8%2F8614ae1baa69934ae70080408029164e.jpg&h=428ae595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個屋苑於網上引起網民熱議，不少網民更仿傚做法，提出其他極具創意和味道的屋苑名稱，如「小澤園」、「吉宅名埗」等，亦有人笑言該屋苑的住戶可以明正言順表示自己睡在「三上悠雅」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/3/31ce82439a3a7428c5b9acc10dc5710d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F3%2F31ce82439a3a7428c5b9acc10dc5710d.jpg&h=95811aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/7/73078779cc6ba29a6057bb5c8ea3a75d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F7%2F73078779cc6ba29a6057bb5c8ea3a75d.jpg&h=8ad85a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/7/7b3923555058ccc6da9eca074f686c35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F7%2F7b3923555058ccc6da9eca074f686c35.jpg&h=0b1780e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/d/d45cd37dc2a9107b7aeb57f67e429937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2Fd%2Fd45cd37dc2a9107b7aeb57f67e429937.jpg&h=d84299e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「三上悠雅」是大雅區今年售價最低的新樓盤，單位介乎 1,030 呎至 1,250 呎，售價由 538 萬新台幣 ( 折合約 137 萬港元 ) 至 1,260 萬新台幣 ( 折合約 320 萬港元 ) 不等，如果在香港買不起樓的話，你又會否考慮在這裡置業，感受一下「悠雅」的氣息呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/09/d/dbca1252b2b5c1fa7f785c4ec5fae998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2Fd%2Fdbca1252b2b5c1fa7f785c4ec5fae998.jpg&h=a676cce5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e421431ccd84fde95a2d20cf753c2dece649f3cb","tid":897765,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"小澤園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e59cd6ccbde3006eee764d4f48c26f852f382b0","tid":897765,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"台灣真係淫亂之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e521054f24ff6bf0bec95af8013b07fadb877d1","tid":897765,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"老闆梗緊無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e405315a54f06d45602153fe24cac3eb31cea771","tid":897765,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e0f82f194bac2181d207e53fba05eb50e